	(text "board contact 18650 holders (like Keystone 1043) can generally only go up to 3-5A max\nso 2 in parallel allow up to 10A continous from the full supply (no dc/dc). Hence, I decided to pick a direct connection\nsolderable to the board, which will hopefully heat up less. Will use large copper pours."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 24.384 116.332 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "34ab64a8-d2de-40bb-8188-4657436e6ed5")
	)
